  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For 28 years we at Yachana Foundation have put education as the key to a brighter future for Amazon youth. We are giving free tuition to community-oriented students this year. Our boarding students call themselves Yachana Future Builders [YFB]. Your contribution to offset YFB&apos;s tuition is your key to assure these indigenous and mestizo &quot;builders&quot; are equipped to reverse generations of poverty, practice environmental awareness, and act as stewards of Ecuador&apos;s rainforest.</narrative>
  </description>
